description:
Black Terror believes that his old sidekick Tim is being held at the White House. Terror launches his own personal one-man assault on President West to save Tim.

Issue #2 features the Black Terror in a full-on rage as he takes the battle to the head of state - the President of the United States! Does President West hold the clue to the whereabouts of The Terror's missing sidekick Tim? For his sake, we sure hope not!
name: The Black Terror Goes To Washington, Part Two

description:
A History of Violence begins with two hitch-hikers asking for a lift. The driver and his accompalice proceeds to shoot both of them, and steal their wallets. Both of the men arrive at Tom Mckenneys soda shop, and decide to rob it. During the course of their attemptd robbing, Tom shoots one of them with their own gun, and knocks the other out stone cold.

The domino effect of his vigilantism is a huge amount of media attention and being labelled as a hero, when all he wants is peace and quiet. The other effect of this is the public notoriety he gains. It draws the attention of an old mob boss (Torrino). Torrino begins to stalk him throughout the town with his large black car, and eventually comes inside the soda shop asking to speak with Tom. He does, and he implies that he knows something about Tom's past, to the annoyance of Tom's wife. He also brandishes toms missing finger, which he has kept in a small vial. He is kicked out of the shop by both Tom and his wife, all the while Tom insisting that he has never seen either of them in his life before.
name: A History of Violence

description: Frank Sharp wasn't blessed with good looksin fact, he's probably one of the ugliest men alive. Fortunately, nature balanced that by giving him the unique ability to make people do whatever he wants, just by shaking their hands. Frank uses his gift to work his way through Gotham's worlds of politics and crimebut how long will it be before Batman comes calling?
name: Irresistible Part 1 of 3

volume.name: Batman: Legends of the Dark Knight

description: John Constantine's investigation into his ex-girlfriend Isabel's brutal murder takes him into the deepest bowels of London, where he has a rendezvous with an old friend. "Haunted" part 2.
name: Haunted, Part 2

description: Ever since he came to Earth, Sonic has been saving the day and becoming a worldwide hero! But not everyone is happy with our hedgehog's heroics - and they're going to do something about it! What is this alliance of evil bent on Sonic's destruction, and where have we seen its members before? Can Sonic unravel the mystery before it is too late?
name: Hedgehogging Their Bets
Target for Outlaws : A Lone Ranger Adventure

description: Kate Spencer never shies away from controversy, either as an attorney or as Manhunter. But when super-powered fanatics start murdering doctors in the name of God, "controversy" doesn't begin to cover it. This shocking new storyline hits Manhunter closer to home than she expects!
name: Some Years Later. Part 1: Family Business

description: Its eighteenth century Europe. A besieged city is getting bombarded with cannon ball fire from the Sultan and his Turkish army. However, for the citizens of this crumbling city, a play is being performed within its walls, called "The Adventures of Baron Munchausen." When the real Baron arrives in the midst of this play, he must prove who he is to the audience, and tell of the real adventure as to why he's responsible for the Sultans attack on this city.

The Baron and Sally wind up on the moon and meet the flying head of the King of the Moon, Ray De'Tutto. The king's body recaptures his head and imprisons him in a floating cage, along with Berthold, his servant, the fastest man alive. Freed by the queen's head, Ray discovers it and chases after him on Sybil, a three-headed winged monster. He almost gets them with a giant asparagus spear, but they split up and the monster tries to as well. It explodes in flames and crashes, killing the king's body. They use a lock of the queens hair to try to climb down to Earth, but it is too short and the Baron tries to cut off the top and tie it to the bottom, but this does not work and they plummet towards the Earth.

name: The Warriors Three, Damlog, The Last Laugh

description: An action/adventure tale of the French Legionnaire soldier, Battron, "a man without a country", who is involved with the liberation of a freebooting French ship, the Martel, from a heavily guarded Vichy French port during World War II. The Allies want the ship destroyed; the Germans have sent serious resources and firepower to save it and keep it afloat. But a critical security leak in British intelligence could jeopardize not only the mission but Battrons life. The key is the beautiful former mistress of the Martels captain, enlisted in the hope she can convince him to join the Free French movement with his ship.

volume.name: Belle Starr: Queen Of The Bandits

description:
Blackpool, Vermont, home of organic farmers, fine maple syrup, and the prestigious Dunsany College.

But, as freshman Annabelle MacAleister is about to discover, something very strange is going on in the town of Blackpool, having something to do with the lake that shares its name...
name: "Sacrifice" Part 1 of 3

description: Stranded in the North African desert, Battron and his skilled commandos must try to complete their mission before the luming shadow of the Allied invasion of North Africa. And in order to complete it they will will have to pull off a daring bank robbery in broad daylight. But is the Martel's ship captain's mistress telling them all she knows and whose side she is really on? The World War II action/adventure tale of the French Legionnaire soldier, Battron, continues.

The exciting conclusion to this Battron World War II action/adventure. With most of his men captured by the Germans, Battron puts in motion the final pieces of plan in an all or nothing attempt to secure the French ship Martel and bring it into Allied hands. As things swirl around between the Free French, the Germans, and the German occupied French Vichy, a new player enters the fray...the Americans. Battron is caught between all of them in an attempt to secure the ship Martel they all are desperate to obtain.

... a few more wrinkles to the mystery surrounding the legendary western outlaw's untimely demise. BELLE STARR's biographer, having witnessed her murder, attempts to bring closure to a tragic story. But the closer he comes to discovering the identity of Belle's assassin, the more his own life is at risk.

volume.name: Belle Starr: Queen Of The Bandits

description: It starts out with Sector 7 revealing that they had found a decepticon named Wreckage and begin to reactivate him. It then switches to the Autobots finishing up the battle in Mission City and any other business there as Optimus gives further orders. Then Lennox departs with Simmons who then offers him to join him which Lennox declines. The Autobots and military meet up and discuss plans to dispose of the dead Decepticons as well as the surviving Decepticons, Barricade and Starscream. Barricade is seen giving a signal hoping for a Decepticon to receive it while Starscream receives it while marking himself with strange symbols and talking to himself about other Decepticons and Autobots.
name: Issue Number One

volume.name: Transformers: Revenge of the Fallen Movie Prequel: Alliance

description: Wrestle a Yeti? Easy! Swim with Nessie? Child's play! Get the last word with your wife? never! For exotic adventures the world over, join Cryptozoologist Tork Darwyn, his beautiful wife Tara and a basement full of Cave Monkeys! Wild creatures! Savage battles! And that's just a visit to the in-laws. Two complete stories in this first issue of the popular web comic by artists of Insight Studios.
